/*+ NoMergeJoin(mk k) NoHashJoin(k mk t) NoMergeJoin(k mk t cc) NoMergeJoin(cc k mk t cct1) NoHashJoin(cc cct1 k mk t kt) NoHashJoin(cc cct1 k kt mk t mi) NoMergeJoin(cc cct1 k kt mi mk t it1) NoMergeJoin(cc cct1 it1 k kt mc mi mk t cn) NoMergeJoin(cc cct1 cn it1 k kt mc mi mk t ct) */ select min(kt.kind) AS movie_kind,
min(t.title) AS complete_nerdy_internet_movie
from movie_keyword AS mk
inner join keyword AS k
on k.id = mk.keyword_id AND k.keyword IN ('nerd',
'loner',
'alienation',
'dignity')
inner join title AS t
on t.id = mk.movie_id AND t.production_year > 2000
inner join complete_cast AS cc
on mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND t.id = cc.movie_id
inner join comp_cast_type AS cct1
on cct1.id = cc.status_id AND cct1.kind = 'complete+verified'
inner join kind_type AS kt
on kt.id = t.kind_id AND kt.kind IN ('movie')
inner join movie_info AS mi
on mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND t.id = mi.movie_id AND mi.note like '%internet%' AND mi.info like 'USA:% 200%'
inner join info_type AS it1
on it1.id = mi.info_type_id AND it1.info = 'release dates'
inner join movie_companies AS mc
on mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = mc.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mc.movie_id AND t.id = mc.movie_id
inner join company_name AS cn
on cn.id = mc.company_id AND cn.country_code = '[us]'
inner join company_type AS ct
on ct.id = mc.company_type_id;
